; Name ..........:MilkingAttackStructure
; Description ...:Attack structures
; Syntax ........:MilkingAttackStructure($vectstr)
; Parameters ....:$vectstr-buildings coordinates
; Return values .:None
; Author ........: Sardo (2016)
